name: Constellations
description:
Constellations of randomly generated shapes.

Press "R" to regenerate new constellation.

There are 2 mouse click modes:
- Create random star
- Create ripple 
on where you click.

You can change mode with "space". There will be a short flash when you do.
Use the slider to determine the max distance for the constellations to bond.

Press "E" to empty the space.
Press "S" to save the image.
Press "P" to show/hide particles.
